Why Affinity





Affinity Investment Advisors, LLC, is an independent, registered investment advisor headquartered in Irvine, CA with an additional office in Pennsylvania.  We are a client-centric firm where integrity, transparency, and accountability are integral to the culture of partnership that guides our internal and external interactions.  Affinity has been managing active equity portfolios for institutional and private clients since 1992. 
 




